Title: edu.yale.som.sitefinity.autogen
Description:
The edu.yale.som.sitefinity.autogen .NET solution:
* Provides a user control interface to auto generate and configure a hierarchy of pages, their controls, resources (libraries, categories, tags, etc.) within Sitefinity based on an XML config file.
